{"tid":1494681,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【放鬆一下】連登第一盤圍棋車輪戰","createTime":"2019-08-21T17:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:11:29.000Z","uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6412a50f2da03582b81303f291893ace06920fa5","tid":1494681,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"近車香港發生嘅事令人好<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壓抑</span></span>，本人少少地上過七次街、日日mon住新聞，好佩服啲日日發夢嘅勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係希望入到黎嘅各位<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放鬆一下</span></span>，所以不如一齊黎場圍棋車輪戰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">識唔識玩都可以一齊參加</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n規則如下：<br />\n1.圍棋規則（19&times;19，貼7.5目）<br />\n2.本人一手、<span style=\"color: red;\">最早作有效回覆嘅一手</span>，如此類推⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n我：q16<br />\n#2:  lm<br />\n#3:  q20<br />\n#4:  d16<br />\n#5:  d4<br />\n咁最早有效回覆就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">d16</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後就到我落子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉得幾多得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比個棋盤大家睇吓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFtsjGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFtsjGn.png&h=102622b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：實力8k左右，志在一齊玩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4851bd64673dc056010cd97e4fc106c80eb309","tid":1494681,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"Sorry 真係無心機玩<br />\n大家岩岩先博完命<br />\n今晚應該又訓唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fca7b0d54dd5ca72c4362dd87c20b3125dfc08c","tid":1494681,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"我先，q16。仲有，請大家不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e078be72324f9757c5dec530fe79bbb621043b","tid":1494681,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"R3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd98f16471ef06af1883e2ab2e38cbd5ffb67d2f","tid":1494681,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4851bd64673dc056010cd97e4fc106c80eb309","tid":1494681,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"Sorry 真係無心機玩<br />\n大家岩岩先博完命<br />\n今晚應該又訓唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"食個宵夜早啲訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8774571b77fea6d80c1ed690f66a122d0ba98031","tid":1494681,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"d16"},{"pid":"5597977ccab576f7c8fba409dd6467a3ce86f70d","tid":1494681,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"E3"},{"pid":"af5337e025a6de8a841c60889091ea76fa776f19","tid":1494681,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"c4"},{"pid":"4ae855d437a0d9cada679cb4aa227343127952f6","tid":1494681,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:03:02.000Z","msg":"D5"},{"pid":"3e1d8f624694e7f84ccebcbd4c35c67add6a0f97","tid":1494681,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"利申一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0147340ca9c